# ============================================================================
# dist/ is INTENTIONALLY committed in this repo. This fork is consumed via
# `github:limehawk/React95` in consumer package.json files, and git
# dependencies do not run build scripts — so the built output must ship in
# the tree. See CLAUDE.md "Scope" + "Build Output" sections.
#
# Do NOT add `dist` as an ignore rule. Do NOT run gitignore-builder here —
# the generic Node template adds `dist`, which silently breaks incremental
# dist/ commits for new files.
# ============================================================================
!/dist
!/dist/**

# ===== Managed by gitignore-builder — do not edit below this line =====
